rdf:Description.lla:note: Date of registry of indenture: 1862-01-24, Newport.

Master Cert No. 74185. Ship's log 1863-07-21: William bale Master fell on deck on his own feet and broke his leg. July 22 Put into Falmouth and landed him to the sailors home infirmary. Signed John Davies and John Richards.
Super-cargo; landed and relinquished the voyage at Milford.
